<h3>Payment Received - Thank You!</h3>
<p>We've received your payment for invoice <strong>{{invoiceNo}}</strong>.</p>
<p><strong>Amount Paid:</strong> {{formatCurrency amountPaid}}</p>
<p><strong>Balance Due:</strong> {{formatCurrency balanceDue}}</p>
<p><strong>Payment Method:</strong> {{paymentMethod}}</p>
<p><strong>Paid At:</strong> {{paidAt}}</p>

{{#if balanceDue}}
<p>Please submit your remaining balance at your earliest convenience.</p>
<a href="{{paymentLink}}">Pay Remaining Balance</a>
{{else}}
<p>Your invoice is now fully paid. Thank you for your business!</p>
{{/if}}